<HEADLINE> China Should Expand Mineral Resources Development: Minister (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
China has built a group of large-scale iron and steel
production bases, such as the Anshan Iron and Steel Company Group
in northeast China's Liaoning Province, Wuhan Iron and Steel
Company Group in central China's Hubei Province. A number of large
