<BODY>
<HEADLINE> 40 Teams to Climb 19 Peaks of Nepal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, August 20 (Xinhua) -- A total of 40 expedition teams
has got permission to climb 19 different peaks of Nepal in the
coming autumn season from September 1 to November 15.
</P>
<P>
A Franch team and a Mexican squad have been respectively
permitted to climb the 8,848-meter-high Mt. Qomolangma, the
highest peak of the world, said a press release issued Wednesday
by Nepali Ministry of Tourism and Civil Aviation.
</P>
<P>
The rest target peaks include four above 6,500 meters, nine
above 7,100 meters and five over 8,000 meters, the release said.
</P>
<P>
The 40 expedition teams, which have a total of 289 members,
come from Australia, Austria, Britain, Czech Republic, Denmark,
France, Germany, Italy, Japan, Mexico, Netherlands, Slovakia,
Slovenia, Spain, Switzerland, Ukraine and the United States.
</P>
<P>
Forty-eight expeditions were permitted to climb peaks of Nepal
during the spring season which lasted from March 1 to May 31.
</P>
<P>
A total of 47 climbers scaled Mt. Qomolangma during the spring
season. Seven mountaineers lost their lives during this
season. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970820.0128 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-08-20 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Commentary: Tremendous Contributions of Deng Xiaoping's Theory (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In contemporary China, it can be said that to adhere to genuine
Marxism and Mao Zedong Thoughts is to persevere in Deng Xiaoping's
theory.
</P>
<P>
The CPC Central Committee in the past five years urged party
cadres to stress learning, politics and healthy practices, and has
taken a number of important steps to push forward the study and
promotion of Deng's theory.
</P>
<P>
According to statistics, 21 million officials nationwide,
including 390,000 at or above the county or division level and
1,200 of ministerial or provincial level, enrolled in various of
research forums and study courses. Consequently, an upsurge of
theoretical study led by leading officials has emerged throughout
China.
</P>
<P>
The CPC Central Committee has given approval to the founding of
five bases for the theoretical study of Deng's theory, in the
Central Party School, Chinese Academy of Social Sciences, the
State Education Commission, the University of National Defense and
the Shanghai Academy of Social Sciences. Theoretical researchers
are now actively involved in projects.
</P>
<P>
The CPC Central Committee in the past five years followed
Deng's theory in a comprehensive, appropriate and active
way. Taking into account the reality of contemporary China and new
practices adopted to suit its ever-changing situation, the CPC
Central Committee has formulated the principle of "seizing
opportunities, deepening reform, furthering the opening-up,
promote development and maintaining stability."
</P>
<P>
After a thorough analysis of 12 major issues that would prove
fatal to China's socialist construction, the party urged that the
handling of the areas of reform, development and stability and
strengthen macro-adjustment be handled correctly.
</P>
<P>
In the economic realm, the party advanced the reform in
financial, foreign trade, investment and taxation sectors and
adopted a new development strategy that emphasized sustained
growth and the role played by scientific progress.
</P>
<P>
In the domain of politics, the party put more effort into the
fight against corruption, criminal activities and other social
evil phenomena.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> XIE19970820.0129 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1997-08-20 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Xinhua Commentary: Tremendous Contributions of Deng's Theory (3) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Using the theory as a guideline, the commentary said, the
Chinese people achieved a higher level of understanding, unity of
thought, and boosted morale.
</P>
<P>
Also as a result, patriotism, collectivism, and socialism
received full play in the country, accompanied by an improved
sense of independence and self-reliance, competition, efficiency,
creativity and a better understanding of democracy and the legal
system, it added.
</P>
<P>
Social activities to promote socialist ethical and cultural
progress were also widely held across the country, and were
regarded as an healthy, and inspiring mainspring in the social
life in China, according to the commentary.
</P>
<P>
As President Jiang Zemin once pointed out, the presence of a
guiding principle is of crucial importance, and without such a
backbone, it would be impossible for China to reach the final goal
of the socialism undertaking, because its population is vast, its
level of economic growth as well as the social and cultural
progress are relatively backward, and the competition in the
international arena is fierce, it said.
</P>
<P>
The commentary quoted the final lines of Jiang's speech at the
Party School of the CPC Central Committee in late May, saying that
the Chinese people, during the course of the modernization push,
and the reform and opening-up drive, should hold high the great
banner of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with
China's own characteristics, and practice the theory in various
fields of work as well as in the entire cause of the country.
</P>
</TEXT>
