enterprises, is made public, authorities concerned will have the
right to withdraw a license for an enterprise if it does not
comply the standard.
</P>
<P>
Deteriorating hygiene condition in butcheries in the surburbs of
Kampala has caused concern among the residents.
</P>
<P>
Muhumuza advised residents not to buy food from unlicensed
businesses. 
