<HEADLINE> Asia-Pacific Justice Ministers to Meet in Manila </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, August 20 (Xinhua) -- Chief justices and justice
ministers from Asia and Pacific will gather here for a roundtable
meeting next Monday to discuss legal and judicial reforms in the
region.
</P>
<P>
