<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, August 20 (Xinhua) -- At least 14 people were found
dead and scores of others were still missing after a dugout
overturned in Brantas river in Indonesia's East Java provincial
capital of Surabaya Tuesday evening.
</P>
